{"reponsecode": 0, "reponsemessage": "", "data": {"exhibit_id": "ahbwysjy_museum_xgdx_dikw", "exhibition_name": "安徽文明史陈列（一）", "location": "0,0", "name": "曲水流觞", "size": "", "like": 0, "share_url": "mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=3422", "is_favorited": 0, "_3d_url": "", "description": "这是中国古代民间的一种传统习俗，后来发展成为文人墨客诗酒唱酬的一种雅事。每年的夏历三月上巳日，也就是农历三月初三，人们坐在河渠两旁，在上游放置酒杯，酒杯顺流而下，停在谁的面前，谁就取杯饮酒，意为除去灾祸不吉。 “曲水流觞” 主要有两大作用，一是欢庆和娱乐，二是祈福免灾。在绍兴，“曲水流觞”这种饮酒咏诗的雅俗历经千年，一直盛传不衰。", "images": ["content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/X2Z3ZZCjwI_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/zXW6FEoce1_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/4B8aUKZAsu_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/bAzERfCmko_s.webp"], "audio": [], "video": {"videourl": "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/video/mfsMrfXFeg.mp4", "img": "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/LjPPrJNFYi.png"}, "ispaid": 1}}